        <h4>Your Evidence Standards</h4>
        <p>Think about a belief you hold strongly. What evidence would make you reconsider it? Be specific and honest. Now think about a belief you've recently changed. What evidence moved you? Compare the two cases. What makes evidence persuasive to you personally?</p>
