        <span class="exercise-type challenge">Challenge</span>
        <h4>The Backfire Audit</h4>
        <p>Identify a topic where presenting evidence often backfires—where facts seem to make people more resistant rather than more open. Analyze why. What beliefs or values are being threatened? What sources would the audience trust? Design an alternative approach that might reach this audience without triggering defensive reactions.</p>
